<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/138678-does-anyone-have-the-passage-or-at-least">Does anyone have the passage (or at least the page # of it) of the explanation of the translation of &quot;mbele ache?&quot; Trying to dig back through but having a hard time remembering where it is...</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_138678'><a id="like_count_community_question_138678" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/138678?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F60935.Possessing_the_Secret_of_Joy">like</a></span>

